text: Vasugi Maruthamuthu (born 13 June 1968) is a Malaysian taekwondo athlete. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics demonstration.Vasugi Maruthamuthu Biographical information, Olympedia She competed at the 1990 Asian Taekwondo Championships and 1992 Asian Taekwondo Championships, winning two bronze medals MARUTHAMUTHU, Vasugi : Taekwondo Data == References == Category:1968 births
